snippet.title: 12TailsOnline - Official Trailer 2013 (Inter)
snippet.description: 12TailsOnline is a surprised hit MMORPG from Thailand, featuring 12 festive races of tail-heroes and tons of action-packed missions both PvE and PvP. Our International server is coming soon!
